{"tid":1976371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"等緊世界各地識講中文嘅你入嚟（吹水谷）","createTime":"2020-04-17T07:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:42:05.000Z","uid":9178,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17c0699c1b2f12cf51850046efa623fcef6a33b1","tid":1976371,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得好悶阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係咪覺得生活闊子好窄 想搵下機會識下唔同朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱喇啱喇<br />\n全新群組上線喇 新人唔洗驚融入唔到<br />\n歡迎任何正係想吹水嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩想講可以講 唔洗驚要出嚟真人面對<br />\n為你嘅WhatsApp 增添熱鬧氣息<br />\n唔驚冇人搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論你身在香港/世界各地 只要你識中文<br />\n恭候大家光臨！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由選擇參與群聚活動<br />\n唔鍾意就唔好入 唔洗講咁多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/MV4LdfujpNBY4hfu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FMV4LdfujpNBY4hfu8&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU95mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7b4aaed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/MV4LdfujpNBY4hfu8</a>"},{"pid":"ed80b8d5c76e370364168099062af4b24d80ba6f","tid":1976371,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416e8b627cfe77d2da60a430bfead95d1904020c","tid":1976371,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d2896d97ccae93585e445f83b596b3db652eb1","tid":1976371,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df434f7d9d53e7514a8110ff31ef701e8fd5254","tid":1976371,"